'''叶雅伦'''（{{lang-en|'''Alan Yarrow'''}}，{{bd|1951年|6月27日|}}），生於[[马来西亚|马来西亚]][[新山|新山]]，[[英國|英國]]銀行家。他是2014-2015年[[伦敦市市長|伦敦市市長]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-29958996 |title=www.bbc.co.uk |access-date=2014-11-08 |archive-date=2015-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926002617/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-29958996 |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cityam.com/1415453659/lord-mayor-s-show-2014-pictures-procession-through-city-london-alan-yarrow-fiona-woolf |title=www.cityam.com |access-date=2014-11-08 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003134436/http://www.cityam.com/1415453659/lord-mayor-s-show-2014-pictures-procession-through-city-london-alan-yarrow-fiona-woolf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

曾就读于[[哈罗公学|哈罗公学]]，然后进入[[曼徹斯特商學院|曼徹斯特商學院]]。自2009年起擔任{{link-en|英國特許證券與投資協會|Chartered Institute for Securities & Investment}}會長。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ukwhoswho.com/ |title=www.ukwhoswho.com |accessdate=2014-10-15 |archive-date=2008-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080706115321/http://www.ukwhoswho.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

艾伦·亚罗自2007年起代表橋區擔任市議員，2014年10月接替{{link-en|吴斐娜|Fiona Woolf}}獲選為687任伦敦市市长，任期為2014至2015年。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cisi.org/cisiweb2/cisi-news/s-i-review-article/cisi-welcomes-alan-yarrow-as-the-next-lord-mayor-of-the-city-of-london |title=www.cisi.org |access-date=2014-10-15 |archive-date=2016-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160527051338/http://www.cisi.org/cisiweb2/cisi-news/s-i-review-article/cisi-welcomes-alan-yarrow-as-the-next-lord-mayor-of-the-city-of-London |dead-url=no }}</ref>

